Class Common.BackplaneCallbackType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.penthera.virtuososdk.Common.BackplaneCallbackType
  • Enclosing class:
    Common
    public static final class Common.BackplaneCallbackType extends java.lang.Object
    Identifies the type of request or instruction in the IBackplaneObserver callback method. The BackplaneCallbackType is but one of the parameters; it is accompanied with an Integer result value defined in Common.BackplaneResult that can be used to determine success or failure of communication with the Backplane.
    See Also:
    Observers.IBackplaneObserver, Common.BackplaneResult
